channel.title: INDIR3CT - Cocoa (Trap) + A soundpack I put together ;)
channel.description:
Heya!
Just got a track finished up and thought I'd post it here too ;D Make sure to read the description if you can! Thanks https://soundcloud.com/indir3ct/cocoa
P.S. I just put together a little soundpack containing most of the samples I use in my tracks. Alot of artists have been asking about the diferent snares and brass samples that I use, so I thought I'd put them In a pack. Here is the link, also you can access the Indipack anytime on my soundcloud page. Thanks! [Get Indipack vol. 1 here](https://exit.sc/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1iKu8IOTnd4SEvHBrlnm1XrahtSiN-M7e%3Fusp%3Dsharing)
